291
00:11:40,240 --> 00:11:41,120
What will it take

292
00:11:41,120 --> 00:11:43,580
for you to stop hating the Empress and Lin Mo?

293
00:11:44,640 --> 00:11:46,640
Unless my sister comes back to life.

294
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:48,480
Can you do that?

295
00:12:08,000 --> 00:12:10,040
As long as your sister is resurrected,

296
00:12:10,040 --> 00:12:12,040
you can let go of your hatred, right?

297
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:19,000
Okay.

298
00:12:24,400 --> 00:12:26,240
My demon core has a wood attribute.

299
00:12:26,240 --> 00:12:28,240
It can bring the dead back to life.

300
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,120
Xiaolan.

301
00:12:34,400 --> 00:12:35,360
Young Master.

302
00:12:35,960 --> 00:12:37,490
I don't have much time left.

303
00:12:37,920 --> 00:12:39,640
Let me help you one last time.

304
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:47,640
Your sister still has a trace of true spirit left in her.

305
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,640
With my demon core,

306
00:12:48,640 --> 00:12:49,970
she can be resurrected.

307
00:12:50,560 --> 00:12:52,480
But she will become a demon from now on,

308
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:53,560
no longer human.

309
00:13:00,840 --> 00:13:03,520
You must teach her how to survive among humans.

310
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,280
Han Qingyun.

311
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:07,460
What my young master owed you,

312
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:09,000
I have repaid.

313
00:13:10,040 --> 00:13:10,920
In the future.

314
00:13:11,480 --> 00:13:13,340
You must protect my young master.

315
00:13:24,680 --> 00:13:25,880
What's wrong with me?

316
00:13:27,360 --> 00:13:28,560
What's wrong with me?

317
00:13:29,480 --> 00:13:31,410
These are clearly not my memories.

318
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:34,120
Why am I so sad?

319
00:13:46,360 --> 00:13:47,240
Sister.

320
00:13:47,520 --> 00:13:48,200
Sister!

321
00:13:50,360 --> 00:13:51,160
Brother.

322
00:13:51,640 --> 00:13:52,440
Sister.

323
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:05,400
Are you going back to the capital with us?

324
00:14:05,400 --> 00:14:06,480
I promised Mo Xiaolan

325
00:14:06,480 --> 00:14:07,940
to protect you from now on.

326
00:14:08,600 --> 00:14:10,260
I don't need your protection.

327
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,400
Brother Lin.

328
00:14:11,400 --> 00:14:12,680
You don't have a maid, do you?

329
00:14:12,680 --> 00:14:14,740
I'll be your maid and take care of you.

330
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:15,880
That sounds good.

331
00:14:19,160 --> 00:14:20,420
A maid is unnecessary.

332
00:14:20,560 --> 00:14:21,890
You have hands and feet.

333
00:14:22,920 --> 00:14:24,120
You have hands and feet too.

334
00:14:24,120 --> 00:14:25,760
You probably have countless servants serving you.

335
00:14:25,760 --> 00:14:27,320
You want someone to serve you, right?

336
00:14:27,320 --> 00:14:28,120
My pal...

337
00:14:29,280 --> 00:14:31,640
My mansion has plenty of candidates.

338
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:32,800
When we get back to the capital,

339
00:14:32,800 --> 00:14:34,000
I'll pick two for you.

340
00:14:34,360 --> 00:14:36,480
You can keep those old ladies for yourself.

341
00:14:36,480 --> 00:14:37,280
Lin Mo!

342
00:14:40,000 --> 00:14:40,730
Brother Lin.

343
00:14:40,880 --> 00:14:41,760
You told me last night

344
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:43,400
that the Empress is actually a good ruler,

345
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:45,200
who just has too many involuntary constraints.

346
00:14:45,200 --> 00:14:46,330
How can you prove it?

347
00:14:46,480 --> 00:14:47,280
Well,

348
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:49,120
you'll have to verify it yourself.

349
00:14:49,120 --> 00:14:51,320
If you really want to rid the world of injustice,

350
00:14:51,320 --> 00:14:52,680
I have an opportunity for you.

351
00:14:52,680 --> 00:14:54,000
I wonder if you'd be willing.

352
00:14:54,000 --> 00:14:54,840
And by the way,

353
00:14:54,960 --> 00:14:56,690
you can also verify what I said.

354
00:14:57,040 --> 00:14:57,970
What do you mean?

355
00:14:58,560 --> 00:14:59,280
Take this.

356
00:14:59,400 --> 00:15:01,000
Go to the Dali Court in three days,

357
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:02,600
and someone will give you an assignment.

358
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,960
The Dali Court investigates all officials,

359
00:15:03,960 --> 00:15:05,080
and observes the conditions of the people.

360
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,720
There,

361
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:07,740
you can find the answers you want.

362
00:15:08,160 --> 00:15:09,880
I will go back and reorganize before heading to the capital.

363
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:12,280
See you at the Dali Temple in Fengming City.

364
00:15:18,000 --> 00:15:19,200
Location: Luoxian Town.

365
00:15:19,200 --> 00:15:20,440
Monster: Shamo Ancestor,

366
00:15:20,440 --> 00:15:22,360
Corpse Puppet, Yin Fiend, Wood Monster.

367
00:15:22,360 --> 00:15:22,920
Task:

368
00:15:22,920 --> 00:15:25,120
Clear the monster threat and recruit the Child of Destiny.

369
00:15:25,120 --> 00:15:26,080
Task completed.

370
00:15:26,080 --> 00:15:27,000
Settlement reward:

371
00:15:27,000 --> 00:15:28,920
Strength, agility, and spirit

372
00:15:28,920 --> 00:15:29,920
are greatly increased.

373
00:15:29,920 --> 00:15:31,400
The rewards are quite rich.

374
00:15:31,400 --> 00:15:33,360
Cheat system, you're finally reliable.

375
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:35,240
I can kill a martial arts master with one punch now.

376
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,480
Rule-type items,

377
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:38,330
I'll check them when I get back.

378
00:15:39,800 --> 00:15:40,280
Oh, right.

379
00:15:40,280 --> 00:15:40,880
Xiaoying,

380
00:15:41,080 --> 00:15:43,010
why don't you ride in our carriage?

381
00:15:43,160 --> 00:15:43,720
Lin Mo.

382
00:15:43,720 --> 00:15:45,240
Do you want to die?

383
00:15:45,720 --> 00:15:46,250
Brother.

384
00:15:46,440 --> 00:15:47,280
Brother, come to the capital early.

385
00:15:47,280 --> 00:15:48,340
I'm leaving first.

386
00:15:48,560 --> 00:15:49,160
Xiaoying,

387
00:15:49,400 --> 00:15:50,360
don't cause trouble for them.

388
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,160
I know.

389
00:15:59,560 --> 00:16:00,960
I sent someone to Fengming City

390
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:02,400
to get a new Lin Residence for you.

391
00:16:02,400 --> 00:16:03,560
You can live there from now on.

392
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:04,960
It's also close to the palace.

393
00:16:04,960 --> 00:16:06,760
Let's not call it Lin Residence.

394
00:16:06,800 --> 00:16:07,660
It's annoying.

395
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,370
Let's call it Mo Residence.

396
00:16:09,400 --> 00:16:10,040
Agreed.

397
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,000
From now on,

398
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:14,480
I will be the chief maid of the Mo Residence.

399
00:16:14,640 --> 00:16:15,320
Boy,

400
00:16:15,720 --> 00:16:17,640
can't you see that since this girl came back to life,

401
00:16:17,640 --> 00:16:19,440
she's become more clingy to you?

402
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:22,490
Maybe she's thanking my maid for helping her revive.

403
00:16:23,240 --> 00:16:24,900
Do you believe that yourself?

404
00:16:32,840 --> 00:16:33,880
Mr. Lin,

405
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,280
wait for me!

406
00:16:35,360 --> 00:16:37,620
We'll go hang out with you in the capital.

407
00:16:37,640 --> 00:16:39,040
We've wandered half our lives.

408
00:16:39,040 --> 00:16:41,040
Finally, we have met a wise master.

409
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:43,240
Please let us follow you.

410
00:16:43,240 --> 00:16:44,320
Brothers,

411
00:16:44,520 --> 00:16:45,920
if you two want to go to Baihua Pavilion in the capital,

412
00:16:45,920 --> 00:16:46,800
just go.

413
00:16:47,040 --> 00:16:48,440
Why make up such excuses?

414
00:16:48,640 --> 00:16:49,440
You damn scum!

415
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:49,960
First brother,

416
00:16:49,960 --> 00:16:50,890
second brother,

417
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:52,420
why are you hitting me?

418
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,600
Shouldn't we?

